request.description:
This endpoint makes an HTTP GET request to retrieve a list of categories. The request includes query parameters for pagination, with a limit of 20 categories per page, and a specific category name to search for. The request does not include a request body.

### Request Body

The request does not include a request body.

### Response

Upon successful execution, the endpoint returns a JSON response with a status code of 200. The response body contains an array of category objects, each including an id, name, image URL, creation timestamp, and update timestamp. Additionally, the response includes metadata such as the current page number, last page number, number of categories per page, and the total number of categories.

Example response:

``` json
{
    "status": 200,
    "message": "success",
    "data": [
        {
            "id": 20,
            "name": "Gabrielle Nader",
            "image_url": "https://via.placeholder.com/640x480.png/00aa11?text=ullam",
            "created_at": "2024-08-17T14:16:40.000000Z",
            "updated_at": "2024-08-17T14:16:40.000000Z"
        }
    ],
    "meta": {
        "current_page": 1,
        "last_page": 1,
        "per_page": 20,
        "total": 1
    }
}

 ```

request.description:
This endpoint makes an HTTP GET request to retrieve a list of categories. The request includes query parameters for pagination, with a limit of 20 categories per page, and a specific category name to search for. The request does not include a request body.

### Request Body

The request does not include a request body.

### Response

Upon successful execution, the endpoint returns a JSON response with a status code of 200. The response body contains an array of category objects, each including an id, name, image URL, creation timestamp, and update timestamp. Additionally, the response includes metadata such as the current page number, last page number, number of categories per page, and the total number of categories.

Example response:

``` json
{
    "status": 200,
    "message": "success",
    "data": [
        {
            "id": 20,
            "name": "Gabrielle Nader",
            "image_url": "https://via.placeholder.com/640x480.png/00aa11?text=ullam",

        }
    ],
    "meta": {
        "current_page": 1,
        "last_page": 1,
        "per_page": 20,
        "total": 1
    }
}
